Package services

This package contains all services and business logic required for the app's proper functioning
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SearchService
    Service for searching videos on YouTube and storing the search results for a user session.
    SearchServiceTest
    Test class for SearchService
    SentimentAnalyzer
    Provides methods for analyzing the overall sentiment of a list of videos based on their descriptions.
    SentimentAnalyzerTest
    Unit tests for the SentimentAnalyzer class.
    SentimentWords
    Provides predefined sets of words associated with "happy" and "sad" sentiments.
    SentimentWordsTest
    Unit tests for analyzing the sentiment words using the SentimentAnalyzer class.
    StatisticsService
    Service for calculating word frequency statistics from video descriptions
    StatisticsServiceTest
    Unit tests for StatisticsService class
    YoutubeService
    Service for interacting with the YouTube API
    YoutubeServiceTest
    Test class for YoutubeService
